{"route":{"route":"/posts/1755854433972/","outputPath":"posts/1755854433972/index.html","kind":"post","title":"QdrantでHybrid Search","language":"ja","params":{"abbrlink":"1755854433972"}},"description":"密ベクトルは現在ではText Embeddingサービスやvllmなどを使えば簡単に生成をてきる。 疎ベクトルは色々と探しましたが、直接利用できるサービスがあまりはない、自分で用意しなければならない。 Qdrantが提供するfastembedは利用できますけど、対応している疎ベクトルモデルが少ないため、最後的にsent","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/QdrantでHybrid-Search.md","route":"/posts/1755854433972/","abbrlink":"1755854433972","title":"QdrantでHybrid Search","date":"2025-08-22 17:20:33","updated":"2025-08-22 17:20:33","tags":["llm","rag","text embedding","sparse vector","vector database","hybrid search"],"categories":["llm"],"language":"ja","htmlLang":"ja","locale":"ja_JP","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"ja-JP","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>密ベクトルは現在ではText Embeddingサービスや<code>vllm</code>などを使えば簡単に生成をてきる。<br>\n疎ベクトルは色々と探しましたが、直接利用できるサービスがあまりはない、自分で用意しなければならない。<br>\n<code>Qdrant</code>が提供する<code>fastembed</code>は利用できますけど、対応している疎ベクトルモデルが少ないため、最後的に<code>sentence_transformers</code>の<code>SparseEncoder</code>を利用することにしました。</p>\n<p>例えば、以下のようなドキュメントがあるとします：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">docx = [</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test1&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test2&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test3&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test4&quot;</span>,</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>戻り値の形式がわかりにくく、少し混乱しました：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">document_embeddings.coalesce().indices().cpu().numpy() = </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    [[ <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span> ] [ <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">25</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">29</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">56</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">4035</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">4038</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">4059</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">98</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">67</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">54</span>]]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">document_embeddings.coalesce().values().cpu().numpy() = </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    [<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03429046</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.02966345</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03258647</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03258648</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03258649</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03137818</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.0306967</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.04750843</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.0475084</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.0475085</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03258612</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03137328</span>]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Qdrant疎ベクトル形式の引数要求は以下のようになります：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">indices = [ <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>   <span class=\"hljs-number\">25</span>   <span class=\"hljs-number\">29</span> ... ]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">values =  [ <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03429046</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.02966345</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.03258647</span> ... ]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>最後はなんとかわかりました、実は：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>indices</code>の1次元目が <code>0</code> の要素が、<code>docs[0]</code> (“test1”) に対応します。</li>\n<li><code>indices</code>の1次元目が <code>1</code> の要素が、<code>docs[1]</code> (“test2”) に対応します。</li>\n<li>…</li>\n</ul>\n<p>したがって、疎ベクトルは以下のようになります。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>test1</code>\n<ul>\n<li>indicesは<code>[5 25 29 56 4035]</code></li>\n<li>valuesは <code>[0.03429046 0.02966345 0.03258647 0.03258648]</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>test2</code>\n<ul>\n<li>indicesは<code>[4035 4038 4059]</code></li>\n<li>valuesは <code>[0.03258649 0.03137818 0.0306967]</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>…</li>\n<li>…</li>\n</ul>\n<p>以下は実装した例のコードです。<code>FastAPI</code>でhttpサービスを提供します。</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># sentence_transformersはtorchを依存している</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># intelのMacはもうtorchを利用できないです、LinuxやArmのMacは必要です</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> sentence_transformers <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> SparseEncoder</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> uvicorn</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> pydantic <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> BaseModel</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> fastapi <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> FastAPI</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> typing <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-type\">List</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextResponse</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_ inherited__\">BaseModel</span>):</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    values: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">list</span>[<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">float</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    indices: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">list</span>[<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">int</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextRequest</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_ inherited__\">BaseModel</span>):</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    text: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">list</span>[<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">str</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    query: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">bool</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">False</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">app = FastAPI()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">@app.post(<span class=\"hljs-params\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/sparse_embedding&quot;</span></span>)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">sparse_embedding</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">req: TextRequest</span>):</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> req.query:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># クエリー時はencode_queryを推薦するみたいです</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        document_embeddings = model.encode_query(req.text)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">27</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        document_embeddings = model.encode_document(req.text)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">28</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">29</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># torchのTesnorをnumpy配列に変換する</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">30</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    indices = document_embeddings.coalesce().indices().cpu().numpy()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">31</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    values = document_embeddings.coalesce().values().cpu().numpy()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">32</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">33</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    indices_index = indices[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>].tolist()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">34</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    indices_value = indices[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>].tolist()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">35</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">36</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    data: <span class=\"hljs-type\">List</span>[TextResponse] = [</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">37</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        TextResponse(indices=[], values=[]) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> _ <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(req.text))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">38</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    ]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">39</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">40</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># indexを基に、対応するindicesとvaluesを抽出します</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">41</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> index, i <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">enumerate</span>(indices_index):</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">42</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        data[i].indices.append(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">int</span>(indices_value[index]))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">43</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        data[i].values.append(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">float</span>(values[index]))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">44</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">45</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> data</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">46</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">47</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">48</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">model = SparseEncoder(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">49</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># オフライン環境では、モデルフィルが格納されたディレクトリを指定します、例え：/data/splade-v3</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">50</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;naver/splade-v3&quot;</span>, device=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;cuda:&quot;</span> + <span class=\"